      "title": "Purchase fuel with dollars: CPC announces",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ceylon Petroleum Corporation (CPC) announced the online registration facility for any company or industry that can pay in US dollars to open a consumer account at CPC to obtain a weekly guaranteed fuel quota.",
        "The CPC requested the individual or organization to visit the USD consumer online registration on the CPC official website to complete their registration.",
        "The website has mentioned the list of basic infrastructure requirements for consumer points. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
